Interface DirectoryStatus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DirectoryMsg, MsgBase

    public interface DirectoryStatus
extends DirectoryMsg
    The RDM Directory Status. Used by an OMM Provider to indicate changes to the Directory stream.
